    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 0,
    "last_activity_date" : 1571751837,
    "creation_date" : 1571751837,
    "answer_id" : 58505710,
    "question_id" : 58498344,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Solution: <code>EventSource</code> in angular takes <code>Content-Type : text/event-stream</code> by default. So I created new method and added <code>@RequestHeader(value = \"Content-Type\", defaultValue = \"text/event-stream\")</code> as parameter.</p>\n"
  }, {
