    "answer_id" : 70533321,
    "question_id" : 58498344,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Automatic conversion of Objects are neglected if you don't have getter method for the return type object. If you don't have getter method for <code>GenericApiResponse</code> object add one.</p>\n"
  } ],
